Included here is a prototype layout for a controller circuit.

The uControl board is different from the previous versions and 
requires a different firmware than the other versions.

Features are:
--------------
Support for 3 bipolar steppers using A4988 Polulu driver modules.
Support for 1 servo
Support for 8 input lines 6 bare, 2 as switch inputs
Support for 1 high load output (5A/PWM)
Support for breakout of serial and reset lines

uControl_v1.sch
----------------
  The layout schematic file

uControl_v1.brd
----------------
  The layout source file (just the layout)

uControl_v1.ps, uControl_v1.pdf
--------------------------------
  Exported layout formats of the above board

